13:35.640 --> 13:42.200
with the arrival of spring is dedicated to the conservation of America's wildlife resources,

13:42.200 --> 13:49.720
our natural resources, our soils, waters, forest minerals and wildlife and general. The theme of this

13:49.720 --> 13:57.960
year's National Wildlife Week observance is save America's wetlands. Some might say why

