28:55.560 --> 29:01.640
to tell you the general philosophy behind all of the votes that I have cast. That is that the

29:01.640 --> 29:07.080
greatness and the main thing in this country is not our material things however important they may be

29:07.720 --> 29:15.320
but our good hardworking religious people and I've always tried to sponsor and promote and aid

29:15.320 --> 29:19.960
causes which would give the average man and woman of this nation a better opportunity

29:19.960 --> 29:25.640
to participate in government to make a better living and to educate his children and on that

29:25.640 --> 29:32.360
basis I've always felt that there should be a balance and an equality between labor, agriculture

29:32.520 --> 29:38.520
and industry. I think each has its right plight rightful place and each is entitled to be protected

29:38.520 --> 29:42.360
and I want to see each do well. I think each must do well if we're going to have a

29:43.000 --> 29:50.040
forward looking and a prosperous America. I've always tried to work to see that the working man

29:50.040 --> 29:56.200
got good wages. I don't believe in 50 cent a day wage. I want our working people to have good

29:56.200 --> 30:01.720
working conditions and I have opposed any laws that I thought were intended just to penalize or

30:01.720 --> 30:07.880
strike down the working man or some organization that he might belong to. And I believe sincerely

